p.s:
Illud medium est superficierum parallelarum; 

vel inclinantium.

  This medium has either parallel surfaces, or inclined ones.

div.head:
De flexionibus in sphæra concava;
pro puncto tropico radii remoti.
On reflections in a concave sphere; for the turning point of the remote ray.

p.s:
There is great difference betwixte a corporation privilege for only trade;
& a corporation privilege 

for planting & trade.
